                     <handNote xml:id="h3" script="Ethiopic"> Hand b: <locus from="49ra" to="81ra">49ra-81ra</locus> (Text II, VII-XI): bears some similarity to hand a,
                        but is much more regular. It cannot be excluded that both parts were written
                        by the same
                        scribe.</handNote>
